(base) storm@cernet2:~/test/0$ cat str.out 3.800000 0.000000 0.0000000.000000 3.800000 0.0000000.000000 0.000000 3.8000000.500000 0.000000 0.5000000.500000 0.500000 0.000000-0.000000 0.500000 0.5000001.000000 1.000000 1.000000 Cu
